@startuml MouseManagementSequence
title Mouse speed hotkey flow

actor User as user
participant "hs.hotkey" as hotkey
participant "modules.mouse_management" as mouse
participant "hs.alert" as alert

autonumber

user -> hotkey: press ctrl+cmd+alt+=
hotkey -> mouse: adjustMouseSpeed(0.1)
mouse -> mouse: log warning (not implemented)
mouse -> alert: hs.alert.show("Mouse speed adjustment not available")
alert --> user: informational toast

note right of mouse
Binding skips the description argument, so this helper alert is the sole
user-visible notification even while the feature remains stubbed.
end note

@enduml
